ygData.messageBody:
grats on your level and bp.

reminds me of some events in our guild as well
last week we got our first cleric epic (damn ragefire bottle neck), and he
dinged the same night into 56 i beleive.

and last night was the bday of 2 guildies, one of which got his druid epic
last night too.

Last night in hate i pulled a sage of innoruk by accident 8). I knew i was
going to die probably, but was trying to find a corpse ( i think it
gfluxed). But as i was going towards the corner/up the wall, i started
getting hit abit by a sage of innoruk, she finally came down to main floor,
which the guild promptly pulled after i died, she didnt drop anything
though...

Was fun though 8)

Anwyays, I'm rambling (not my fault guild web site is down right now grrr)

Minkin
Ayonae ro
RIP
